parameters: In battle, commands are entered at the beginning of battle
and then executed in order of the characters' agility.
Once you defeat a monster for the first time, you will be able to see the HP
bars above that type of monster.
The actions characters perform in battle earn them \c[11]TP\fr.
\c[11]TP\fr can be used to perform skills, typically physical ones.
Hampus is a Dark Knight. Dark Knights can heal their party
members using the Transfusion in the Bloodcraft skill category.
Hampus can heal himself using the black magic spell Drain, and can replenish his MP
using Absorb on enemies that have MP.
